    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >生存矿工是一款增量式游戏，你在子弹地狱环境中采矿资源，同时抵御成群敌人的攻击。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2322450/extras/0529911b3d01f502e39127533bd0dba9.poster.avif?t=1770422298\" width=752 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2322450/extras/0529911b3d01f502e39127533bd0dba9.webm?t=1770422298\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2322450/extras/0529911b3d01f502e39127533bd0dba9.mp4?t=1770422298\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你会在短时间内采矿资源，然后要么被敌人击败，要么抵挡足够长时间逃脱并获得额外奖励。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >随后你返回商店，花费资源升级角色并解锁新的关卡和采矿区域。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2322450/extras/99872caa8233fed7796dea23de049a8a.poster.avif?t=1770422298\" width=752 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2322450/extras/99872caa8233fed7796dea23de049a8a.webm?t=1770422298\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2322450/extras/99872caa8233fed7796dea23de049a8a.mp4?t=1770422298\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏玩法 / 特点</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >子弹地狱风格的敌人群战斗</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >采矿收集资源</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >花费资源购买升级和道具</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >增量式进度</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >武器和改装的库存系统</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >随着进度解锁新领地</p></li></ul>",
